        "content": "<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/c4/D6iArzmlhUy89TKMeB9VhOWu/zulip-setting-outline.jpg\">zulip-setting-outline.jpg</a> Did some design for the BOT icon for <a href=\"https://github.com/zulip/zulip/pull/19797\">#19797</a>, also did a few other icons to see how it matches.</p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/c4/D6iArzmlhUy89TKMeB9VhOWu/zulip-setting-outline.jpg\" title=\"zulip-setting-outline.jpg\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/c4/D6iArzmlhUy89TKMeB9VhOWu/zulip-setting-outline.jpg\"></a></div>",
