    {
        "content": "<p>Feels like it is easier to distinguish in  a list. <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"19257\">@Alya Abbott</span></p>",
        "id": 1411958,
        "sender_full_name": "Vlad Korobov",
        "timestamp": 1659009373
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Looks reasonable to me, other than being a little small compared to the others, so I think we'd want to scale it up a bit.</p>",
        "id": 1412034,
        "sender_full_name": "Alya Abbott",
        "timestamp": 1659020972
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>One side thing I notice looking at that screenshot is that the icons aren't vertically aligned properly; generally we want them to be centered within a virtual column, like we have in the gear menu:</p>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/f8/ofvNFkQyVL2J1Vk_He-sn1AY/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/f8/ofvNFkQyVL2J1Vk_He-sn1AY/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/f8/ofvNFkQyVL2J1Vk_He-sn1AY/image.png\"></a></div>",
        "id": 1412525,
        "sender_full_name": "Tim Abbott",
        "timestamp": 1659054496
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>At a technical level, we're going to do 2 changes:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Switch to using <code>zulip-icon-bot</code> for in the menu rather than <code>fa-github</code>.</li>\n<li>Possibly change the SVG for <code>zulip-icon-bot</code> to a different icon. <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"24433\">@Raymond Asogwa</span> can you do a screenshot of your bot icon in the message feed and user profile popover? I think that's the more important setting. <code>static/shared/icons/README.md</code> is worth reading if you've not seen it, since that's our system for adding custom icons.</li>\n<li>Possibly a third change if we find changing the SVG requires a hard refresh to update for folks -- I have a vague recollection of that being an issue the last time we changed our icon font.</li>\n</ul>",
        "id": 1412529,
        "sender_full_name": "Tim Abbott",
        "timestamp": 1659054652
    },
    {
